org.gbif.jetty

Class HttpConnectorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.jetty.HttpConnectorFactory

  • public class HttpConnectorFactory
extends Object
    Factory class that provides instances of the Connectors used by an application. Contains factory methods for the default connectors: application and admin.

    • Method Detail

      • admin

        public static HttpConnectorFactory admin(org.eclipse.jetty.server.Server server)
        Creates an instance of the admin connector. The default values for this instance are: - name: admin - port: 8081 - threadPool: QueuedThreadPool(maxThreadPoolSize)

      • application

        public static HttpConnectorFactory application(org.eclipse.jetty.server.Server server)
        Creates an instance of the application connector. The instance returned is a SelectorChannelConnector which by default has a threadPool implementation. The default values for this instance are: - name: application - port: 8080 - threadPool: none
